<div class="project-text">
    <h3>The Project</h3>
    <p>Serial grillers from Poland who took their obsession seriously enough to design a product around it. The Vulcanus is a high-end barbecue built from a specific metal alloy chosen for one reason: to survive any winter without complaint.</p>
    <p>I designed a new B2B page for them and we are currently working on integrations across the websites of their European retailers.</p>
